Project Summary

Project Information

Field Value
Name SimMetrics
Description A Java library of similarity and distance metrics e.g. Levenshtein distance and Cosine similarity. All similarity metrics return normalized values rather than unbounded similarity scores. Distance metrics return non-negative unbounded scores.
Homepage https://github.com/mpkorstanje/simmetrics
